Interface IRepository<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The entity type this repository manages
All Known Implementing Classes:
ApplicationRepository, EnquiryRepository, ProjectRepository, UserRepository
public interface IRepository<T>
Generic repository interface that defines standard operations for data access across different entity types.
